{"tid":640367,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成地精 「換妻party」滿地套子、性玩具　25男女全裸遭逮","createTime":"2018-04-24T08:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T09:05:18.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a5194fefa8377928db8ce230dd4d660f19d243ef","tid":640367,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T08:35:10.000Z","msg":"根據香港《蘋果》報導，泰國警方21日在芭達雅一間飯店查獲由多名外籍人士舉辦的「換妻性愛派對」，警方突擊搜索發現，飯店的禮堂有11名男性、14名女性全身赤裸正在進行淫歡派對，地上充滿保險套、壯陽藥以及多種情趣玩具等，場面相當混亂。<br />\n據了解，策畫這次活動的是一名53歲中國籍男子，報名者必須提出情侶證明，並接受能在派對中換妻、交換伴侶，報名費收1500泰銖(約新台幣1400元)，參與性愛派對者多是外籍人士，分別有來自中國、新加坡、馬來西亞、德國、泰國、印度、柬埔寨、烏克蘭等，最後泰國警方以「非法組織未經申報的聚眾活動」、「非法組織色情活動」等罪名控告該中國籍男子。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180424/1340286\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180424%2F1340286&d=6rgDRqZdkloq1MaO0jNX48mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=d0558e7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180424%2F1340286&h=8d05594f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180424/1340286</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180424/640_770a70417707a8efe63136993e00ffb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180424%2F640_770a70417707a8efe63136993e00ffb1.jpg&h=87f90196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想揾個ptgf 港女換人妻"},{"pid":"a98e24fcb13f17abc154eecdeaaa877401a7146d","tid":640367,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T08:41:14.000Z","msg":"樓主泛民打手waiwaiwai<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/164111_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F164111_ea3dc39